values:
HELLLLLLLOOOOOOOOOOOOO!!!

Its so F*cking hot I want to kill my self.  Seriously 98 and humid... disgusting I am honestly running around NY in my bathing suit because I can't handel it.

I need a new job.  Why?  Well because I'm getting sucked into what i like to call "Starbucks Life"  It's the point where the money is good enough and I have enough responsibility that I have to put my job befroe my carrer.  Make sense?  SO after 6 happy months I am quitting Starbucks.

bye!
I'm out like a fat kid in  dodge ball

So I'm working my crappy ass boring job that i actually kind of like...counting the minutes until I get to go home and who walks in the door?  HUGH JACKMAN!!!  I died, and after i was recisitated (I konw, I know it's spelt wrong) i said "OH MY GOD your HUGH JACKMAN!!" to which he replied "OH MY GOD I so am!"  I loved it... almost as much as the fact that next week at this time I will be in CA!  Yes thats right ladies and gentelman I'm comming so ALL you losers had better call me or something...  Yeah I'm going to go play volleyball now...bye

so i just donated blood.

What makes cheeks turn pink when it's cold?
Blood. (or giving blood cause I'm definatly a little pink)

yeah except i seriously doubt the competance of the the New York blood center.  SO they stick the needle in my rught arm and leave it there for 5 min.  I'm in alot of pain and no blood is going to the bag.  So they are like "Oppppps... lets try the left arm.."  Yeah so both my arms hurt...bastards.

ONE MOE MONTH OF THE SEMESTER FROM HELL!!!!  Seriously everyone I know has had a break down...  

mine was fun I told a girl "fuck off, your not my teacher, where the hell do you get off corecting me bitch"  in the middel of a class... it was actually kindof amazing...

I come home in JUNE!!!  Whos excited?  

Yeah so anyway I'm losing feeling in my fingers so I'm going to go home.

Hello boys and girls.  It's like a thing once a month I realize I've neglected my live journal and NEED to update it.  I have now reached the ultimate loser status.  Me and my friend thought it would be fun to do one of those dating service profiles since all the guys we know are more intrested in our brothers.  So a half an hour latter (yes it freakin' took a half hour) I finished and was REJECTED!  I was like "WHAT!?!?!" apparently they are unable to match 1 out of 5 people.  Say hello to Miss 20%!  A little pathetic...maybe I should have answered the questions a bit more truthfully.  Oh well only losers do that anyway.  Shut up.  
      So ANYWAY life is good, the weathers warmer I have a job at starbucks.  It is  suprisingly fun.  FAO schwartz hired me too and I was all excited until I found out they pay $5.25 an hour and treat their employees like a sweat shop in China.  Oh! Oh!  I totally get free coffee all the time so I am constantly on a caffeine high at work!  It's kind of amazing!  Ok I'll post again next month. Jeeezzz people call me sometimes...gawd...

So ummm my room mates parents are staying with us for a few days and then I'm going with them to south carolina for a week.  Problem!  THEY ARE CRAZY!!!  Seriously her mother is the most physco controling stage mom ever!  I am toatly freaking out... I should have gone to canada....  Oh well... 
I am now HALF WAY DONE WITH AMDA!!! WHOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOT!

HELLLLLLLLLLOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO  it's been awhile.  I'm not near a computer anymore because I moved to a new fabulose apartment that i LOVE SO MUCH!!  And I've been avoding this buliding cause one of my old room mates thinks I have their charecter skirt and I don't but she is still going physco on me and all my friends... yeah... it's special.  Can I just say that it is so cold!  I mean honstly why can't the weather be like CA?  Seriously it's like 60 there...10 here =(   
Yeah... ummm don't really write anymore I thought i did but no not really... bye!
So umm last night was pretty amazing!!!  Seriously I love you three!  Well Phantom (or as katie would say POTO) blew harder than kevins mom and thats really saying something...

I'm am SO comming home on SATURDY!

I don't have a car though... so it's going to blow.  I'm pretty upset about that.  My car will be sitting in the drivway but  I CAN'T DRIVE IT BECAUSE MY PARENTS CANCELLED MY INSURANCE AND REFUSE TO GET IT INSURED.  Which also means it will be hard to sell the freking thing because no one can test drive it.  Litle pissed.  I won't be able to do anything because like none of you guys drive.  SO i won't get hang out with everyone nearly enough.  Sorry kids. =(

We found a couch today so me and brittany carried it 7 blocks to our NEW apartment.  It was kinda amazing.  My shoulders totally hurt though.

YAY for Kevin, Katie, and Joey for getting called back!!!

Personally I wanted Kevin to be the Stepmom.  A guy played it when we say the New York Opera's version of cinderella (which blew by the way.)

OH! my icon is from "Merrily we Roll along"
For all of those who were confused

In 4 days I will be in my new Apartment.
In 6 days I will be home.

Schweeeet.

I can't wait to be home!  Seriously the past week has gone so slow so I can just imagine how slow this week will be.  I dunno, I kinda think it might be a little weird to be home after being away so long.  I'm expecting everyone and everything to be the same but obviously, in 6 months, things are bound to change.  What I enjoy the most is that I have talked to my brother and gotten to know him better since I moved away.  And my relationship with Coulby has gotten so distant that I can't even tell you anything about him. Funny. Okay, I'm off to dye my hair.

Good night.

December is going to be an AMAZING month!
I move into my new apartment with two of my favorite people ever! (it's kind of weird how I have only known them such a short time and yet I can't imagine life with out them)
AND  I come home for 10 days!!!  (Thats right bitches so we totally need to hang out...call me!)

WHOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOT!!!!

Can I just say that Kevin you are the most amazing person ever?  Seriously ever voice mail I have from you makes me laugh

I'm going with my friend patrick to Toronto for thanksgiving... it should be interesting a 13 hour ride will be special.

so after I get out of re-hab, my kids are really screwed up cause there mother is addicted to crack and their father is gay.  But it's ok, the money I made in the revival of "Their playing our song" will be more than enough to pay for their thaerapy and to get my name changed to just "Renee" like J-lo....

WAY not fair!!!  My jazz class is doing a lame dance to the most annoying song in the world (Mamma Mia) and my friends class is doing the original Rum-tum-tugger dance from Cats.  ::is incredibly jealouse::  Kill me.  I feel like I'm in show choir. 

Oh Kevin I love you you are AMAZING!

Who is SO sunburned that they can barley sit?  Me!

But it was worth it because when it stops being red I will not be as incredibly white and I had so much fun!   Me, Brittany, Ptrick and Megan went to Coonie Island on Monday... it was AMAZING seriously I think it is the most fun I have had since I've been here.  We playd on the beach, went on rides, and ate hot dogs.  It made me miss home so much because the beach reminded me of Ventura... it was kinda sad.

Oh! Oh! I got A's on my past TWO musical theater songs!!!  (Kevin aren't you proud?)   

I hve to go practice jazz now...

Arghhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh
I am one un-happy camper...  I took today off work to go to my STUPID vps teachers STUPID tremoring class and the STUPID women canceled it!  (tremoring is by far the most ridiculouse thing I have ever done in my entire life)


Anyway... I'm comming home Dec. 18th.  We had all or mid terms and I did well in everything except theater dance because the guy makes me SO freakin' nervouse!  He is a nazi, he never smiles, and he's mean!  But I get paid tomrrow so that makes it a great day!  I'll have money!  YES!

"Hi my name is Renee and I'm calling from Playwrights Horizon, How are you this evening?....Good.  I was wondering if you had a minute to hear about or 2004-2005 season that starts August 31"

Yes ladies and gentlemen, I am a tele marketer...234 calls latter I sold NOTHING!!  ARGHHH and I work on commision...NO GOOD!!

Anyway I am having SO much fun.  Ready for a super quick update on EVERYTHING: Adrea came and visited me, we had lunch, it was fun.  Kevin is BY FAR the most amusing person in the world.  I'm going to kill Nick.  Coulby is totally sun burned and looks really cute!  I got a tattoo.  Where did morgan come from? (She NEEDS to call me)  I died my hair.  My song for Musical theater was relly good!  According to my Voice Production and Speech teacher I have a lisp..wtf... OH! and I LOVE my group basically for the things we say...

-"CHASE FOR THE LAST TIME PUT THAT AWAY!!!"
"but...it's my insulin pump..."

-"Step forward and say a chercter you can play right now"
"Heather Headly Aida...oh thats not the characters name?....Rafiki, the Lion King"

-"you put your finger in the hole and you push....it's the p o r n o door!"

Yeah the only people who seem to find any of that remotley funny is Lindsay and I...

Alright good night!
well I had a fabulose post but it got deleted twice...I give up.

Well, I switched programs.  I sang a song from the last five years, and then because I didn't have any other music I had to sing somewhere over the rainbow...  

I like my new group a lot!  

KEVIN IS HERE!!! YAY!!  

Mallory (one of my roomates) and I got in trouble for tapping in our room... that;s the bad thing about our room being right by the lobby...

I have a blister on my blister...is that possible?

I got my first song for musical theater "Some World" from Henery, sweet Henery...I should be learning it right now but I couldn't force myself to anymore...I had to read the show today and listen to the soundrtrack...It was a supprisingly entertaing show.

I have the hugest blister on the bottom of my foot. Why you may ask? Well because the subway routes are different on the weekend and we got of the on train to switch to another, but it was closed so, we decide to go a couple stops past where we really wanted to go so we could switch to the right train and ride it back. SO we get to the exit only to find there are NO trains back the way we needed!!! SO we spent 2 AND HALF hours walking around Soho trying to find the subway station that would take us home... I'm am having SO much fun! I am switching programs (maybe haven't made up my mind yet) so I had to find a song to sing... Placements went well they asked me if I knew who this english actress was Marta or Mara Kuzack or something like that...I didn't know so they said "thank you" and I walked out. I am tottaly feeling ignored by Coulby...he hasn't made any effort to be my friend... I talked to him today (almost in tears)and still he wouldn't tlak to me... I understand we are both making other friends but really...COULBY I GUESS WHAT I WROTE IN THE LETTER TO YOU WAS TRUE EVEN THOUGH WE SPENT AN HOUR TALKING ABOUT HOW IT WASN'T...

AHHHHHHHHH
I'm SO bored and stuck at home with two screaming 7 year olds who seem to feel it necessary to hit me with mylar ballons... Kill me.  I am here for three more days and this is the fun I get to have...

I cleaned my room out today I am so ready to move!  And we put the office back together and moved all coulby's stuff into my room... but yeah SO BORED!!!



SO BORED!!!!!!!

FOUR DAYS!!!!
I'am SO excited!
Graduation yesterday was REALLY boring...I hated it!  We had a party afterwards, basically just family that was ok...I so done with it by 8 but not everyone left until 11...that sucked.

Ok have to help my 7 year old cousin find something to eat...it is always an adventure since he's dad is like a vegan...

SOOOOOOOOOOOO here's the drama that has been my life:
My government teacher says I have 16 unexcused absences (meaning I've ditched 16 times) EXCEPT I have only missed that class about 6 times and they were ALL excused.  Now a normal human being would be some what understanding, and maybe admit that they may have made a mistake...but no.  Mr. Flynn not only refuses to helpful but also says he is going to FAIL me if I do not "clear up some of my absences."  ok fine.  So I have my mom call and try to excuse days when I WASN'T ABSENT and the attendance office won't let her...ARGHHHHHHHHHHHHHH!  SO, she talks to one of the Vice Principals, possible the most stupid person on the planet, who tells my mother there is nothing he can do.  AND since goverment is a required class, if I fail it I don't graduate.  FUCK'IN A!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

SO I've just spent the last twenty minutes trying to figure out how long it takes to get take/get results for the CHSPE and the GED...so that will be fun.  I'm talking to Mr. Flynn tomorrow to see if he is actually going to fail me...if he says he will than I'm dropping out that minute.

AND  I didn't go to work on Friday so my hours got cut!  I only work about 8hrs a week...I was working about 20.   I hate me right now!

well, I sent in my first payment for AMDA today, no yesterday.  so I am offically going.  I guess it never seemed real to me until I mailed the check and filled out the loan application.  I'M SO EXCITED!  And nervous to....I can't wait for school to be over

Anyway...Sound of music opened last weekend.  It's good but LONG!!!  Only 5 more weeks of performances.

And i'm totally cranky b/c it's SO hot!

Got my wisdom teeth out on Friday...I'm counting down the minutes till my next vixaden.... 5 minutes They make me SO tired for an hour and then I spend the next 3 hours bouncy and off the wall. CRAZY!! Yuck...my mom is making me go to school tommorow...I understand I did allot of shit this weekend. Coulby and I styled wigs for "Seusical the Musical", the next play at the club (Coulby's directing) AND cleaned out the costume room and part of backstage at the club. 3 minutes THE FUNNIEST THING EVER was on TV today...we watched a documentary on Tuperware... it was Awesome...ok good night!

What I love is that almost everyone is dreading going home, or spending time with their families... Especially the people coming home from college...I'm amused

OH!  And everyone needs to listen to "A Christmas Carol" on the Radio am 1520 it's on tonight at 5pm and 8pm and tomorow (Christmas!) at 8 am and 4 pm.  It's good! Kevin, Coulby, Linda, and me are all in it!

Merry Christmas Everyone!

"John-Jacob-Jingel-Heimer-Schmidt, thats my name too..."

I never really understood this song...and I still don't.

I'm at Morgans, we are waiting for Tara.  Kill me.  At least twice tonight she will start talking about her dry vagina.

Early Christmas Present of Wicked 
Finishing my stock project in 20 minutes
Getting out of Work Experience EARLY
One more day to Christmas Break
Shopping tonight with Morgan
Signing up for dance classes at Morepark
GETTING A SCHOLARSHIP!

This has been a good morning!

Today has kicked butt!
I'm so excited!  I auditioned for "Snow White" today, and actually did good!
And now I'm going to go shopping with Jenni! (she is running home and then we are leaving, so I'm killing time by updating my journal) It's exciting, I haven't seen her for years!

Last night was so much fun!  Instread of going to Denny's like we do after EVERY show (I'm sick of that place) WE went to Inn-m-Out.  Yummy Shakes and Fries...I turned in a job application but after how loud we were they won't ever hire me... I think me and Kevin sining a couple of lines from the Wild Party over and over didn't help (-Just tell me Berz why after seven years we have never been into the sack before?   -Kate don't bother me. -I'm just asking why -Whenwe met you were less than a DIRTY WHORE!!!)  And yeah, then a bunch of middel schoolers came and we were totaly laughing at them, they were laughing at us, and then I realized one of the little snot rags was my cousin, needless to say I embaressed him throughly!  

Changing gears...
The talent show is tommorow...yuck.  I'm going to suck, but I was okay with that before 'cause me and Coulby were going to do "Sing" and I was going to be in "I wanna be a producer"  but now I'm not so I'm not looking forward to this at all.

Now off to find a new job and go shopping with Jenni!

OH!  Christmas Carol Closes tomorrow!  People need to come see it!

It's amazing how much one person can piss you off *cough*kelly*cough* I hate pop-up's. It would be one thing if they were interesting, or new, a new pop up would be good. It's gotten to the point where I know what pop up it is by the size of the box... Snow white audition tommorow...I still don't know what to sing. I was going to the song I have sang a million times from Kiss me kate but someone forgot me...again. Gezzz Coulby, it's ok, your forgiven. AND I HAVE A BLACK EYE!!! Thanks morgan... AND my key won't open my driver side door half the time so I have to crawl into my car through the passenger door! It's some what pathetic...I feel like Katie. It's been a bad day...now off to work. It took me a half an hour to get their yesterday I HATE TRAFFIC! I HATE CONSTRUCTION THAT CAUSES LOTS OF TRAFFIC!! AND I HATE CAMARILLO!!! I feel better now.

So Coulby drops me off at my house around 10:30, and I see my car covered in saran-wrap...thanks morgan.  But it's okay because I got my revenge, there is nothing better the toilet papering someone's house after it has rained...ummmm...I mean I know nothing...

-Sherry (Morgan's aunt...)

"Do you think I would look good with an accent?"
-Annie Sun

"What's a communism?"
-Annie Sun

"Denmark?  Isn't that in England?"
-Stupid cheerleader in English

Christmas Carol opened last night, it was actually pretty good, only cause Steven wasn't there though.  My favorite part is when we sang Jingel Bell rock in like 8 different keys...yeah, it was special...AND then we thought Sara wasn't going to be there, she's christmas past, so Coulby was going to be her and then she showed up...Morgan, once again, looked like a pedifile, Ryan deserves die, Yeah...ok... There's a plan to kill Ryan by taping child porn to the street and then running him over.  AND we are going to Steven to...if anyone would like to... we're offering $1.50, plus the knowledge you have done the world a favor...

-Stupid girl in Choir

"Yeah so they can buy bolt cutters and steal our bikes?!?"
-Morgan (She say's it was all Brian though...)

"I'm Karl Marx, and I don't care"

Yeah, I should be memorizing Hamlets god damn soliloquy right now but I don't wanna...

Oh! Sioban, Steven ISN'T going to be there one night but were not doomed, cause they guy that does scrooge for the radio is going to come do it...it will probably be our best show!

I hate this..I was writting and all ready to post when I realized I would probably piss someone off with what I wrote. Oh well...

YES!!! Even my father has become slightly annoyed with his family which means we are leaving my grandmas early tommorow YES!!! I am SO bored. I just discovered they had a computer so I've been mildly entetained by seeing which sites there computer would and wouldn't let me go to...apperently hotmail is a bad site...ahhh, I love intenet controls... It took me twenty minutes to convince my cousin I would not break his computer, he was just cranky cause he broke his playstation two, and he has to go to wok tonight. He threw a tantrum. This man is 28 yers old and throwing a tantrum...it was special. Yesterday was...ummm...interesting. My Grandma failed to tell anyone we were going out to dinner for thanksgiving so there was some major confusion and anger. My mom was a little pissed, I was amused. Ok thats enough for me. The room where they have the computer is also where they keep their 3 cats, not only am I allergi to cats but I don't think they have cleaned out the litter box for months. AHH KILL ME I"M SO BORED!!!

ahhhhhhhhhhhhhh one weekend with my grandmother in mormon ville with NOTHING to do with in 50 miles no one under the age of 20, besides me Kill me now. I'm going to be quizzed about Jesus... maybe I should tell her I'm an Egg-nog-stick...that would go over real big... or tell her my opinions about abortion... two years ago one of my cousins said something about mormonism being a cult and he is still being shunned by my grandmother... ah, the memories... I'm going to go pack, Happy Thanksgiving Everyone!!

**YAWN**
I'm tired.
Didn't go to first period cause I didn't go to mock trial last night... it makes sense I swear.
I GOT OUT OF ASB!!!  YES!  Now I have a choir again...ahhh I love my schedule.
I went with Coulby to see Grease at the Civic arts plaza it was cute, but there's the bell...I have to go to choir now.

In...**counts on fingers** eight months I will be leaving Camarillo to go to the American music and Dramatic academy in New York City!!!

YEAH!!!  Both Coulby andI auditioned like a week ago and we both got in... I'm a little excited.

Now I need money...
drug dealing?  
prostitution?  
hmmmmmmm

Today is my birthday and you wanna know what I did?

I DROVE!!!

Anywho, thanks for not putting the vibrator in my locker morgan...I would have killed you.

I auditioned for AMDA this weeken it went fairly well.  I did my monoluges and my interview and went back into the waiting area finnaly relaxed cause it was all over.  BUT NO.  One of the audition people sat down next to me and asked me if I would sing to.  AHHHHHHHHH!!!  But I was like "...ummm k."  So I sang 'Not for life of me' from thouroughly modern millie.  It was... interesting.

AND I saw Into The Woods.  It was SO BAD!!!   The girl who replaced knew a total of FOUR words in the ENTIRE show... but apperently she knew more than me...stupid director.  Oh well after seeing the show I'm even happier I got kicked out because they had six people in the audience and they suxed.
